{"tid":689572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(佛都有火) 中國大佛陷火海！ 高聳佛像如巨大火柴棒狂燒不停","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T09:55:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd22b494c533a73fb2e0a4adda3e38239f9c3b41","tid":689572,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php0XzeiX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php0XzeiX.jpg&h=df5a515f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國甘肅蘭州五泉山龍恩寺興建中的大佛，於2日下午4時55分突然發生大火，只見佛寺內高聳的佛像猶如巨大火柴棒狂燒不停。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，大佛工地起火後，外圍的鷹架和防護網成為助燃物讓火勢延燒，濃煙竄至天際，消防單位於當天下午5時50分撲滅火勢，並無人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n現場燃燒面積約20平方公尺，火災原因與實際損失仍在調查中，有網民聯想到了號稱亞洲最高木塔、四川綿竹市九龍鎮的靈官樓，去年也被一把火燒毀，而龍恩寺大佛和當時的靈官樓一樣，都成了沖天火柱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2446897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446897&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcAU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a533147a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446897&h=4c6c8008\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2446897</a><br />\n<br />\n縁份到了, 自然悶燒都唔益中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e6f7cef56bbb590d124501b77f43d51963c627","tid":689572,"uid":1067,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"佛都有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36582a2cef2a36b73f11ff5dd0a6066dbe87715c","tid":689572,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"唔受班蝗拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d430fe20ab5db0a360cf6e93c7dcf178c43987e","tid":689572,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"本來無一物，何處惹火災"},{"pid":"c771c219171abc54d2c7b8cf96d6b89be5b52c9f","tid":689572,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係古蹟"},{"pid":"45917c7f5b98eeeda43b098c6514f6329da1d570","tid":689572,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"六四，佛都有火"},{"pid":"0b1b6d532c7301a292535826ef4ae066651c4c39","tid":689572,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c8144e2967e3c1a69ea78e9688adafb4da26754","tid":689572,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"風雲火燒樂山大佛"},{"pid":"02518442086d2535fdcb424a37a84c4d574fdc8e","tid":689572,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"佛系即自燃"}]}